name: Fury of the Fur 1 of 1 Collection

metadata.description: The power of FOTF, in the palm of my hand! Created by artist Voxu during the initial FOTF launch as a way to showcase his skills and love for the design, Dr. Tedtavius was upgraded and brought into the collection as a full one of one. Delivered as a special thank you to one random lucky minter.
metadata.name: Dr. Tedtavius
